3.8.2026 R Trogdor Pre-release
Unnecessary files deleted and terrain change proximity bug fixed since last update

To install:

Download Wesnoth
Open Wesnoth, and click on the blue i in the lower left corner of the opening screen.
This will open a pop-up that shows you some file path shortcuts.
Open the one called "Add-ons." 
Place Trogdor_The_Burninator under "Add-ons"
Unzip Trogdor_The_Burninator.
Check that the file opens directly into the correct subfiles.
Close Wesnoth completely.
Reopen Wesnoth.
Select Campaigns from the side menu.
If you scroll through Campaigns, Trogdor should be visible somewhere on the list, probably near the bottom.
